t website, photography and print work.  </p>		The result:		<ul>		<li>Vector logo</li>		<li>Fresh website that is easy for clients and salesforce to use</li>		<li>Professional photographs of their products</li>		<li>High quality product sheets for quick reference</li>		</ul>				 <p>It has been great working for BD Breads and be able to see their new venture take off with success.  I hope to continue doing design work for them in the future.</p>		</div> <!-- close client info --> <div id="wrapper">        <div id="bd-slider-wrapper">            <div id="slider" class="nivoSlider">                <img src="images/bdbreads/bdbreads-home.png" title="#home-title" />                <img src="images/bdbreads/bdbreads-categorypage.png" title="#category-title" />                <img src="images/bdbreads/bdbreads-productpage.png" alt="" title="#product-title" />                <img src="images/bdbreads/bdbreads-contactform.png" alt="" title="#contact-title"/>				<img src="images/bdbreads/breads-hq2.png" alt="" title="#print-title"/>            </div>                                <div id="home-title" class="nivo-html-caption">            	<strong>Homepage</strong><br/>Each of the 5 buttons link to a product category page. I also included a photo slideshow of the launch food show. The client wanted a simple and functional theme for the website.            </div>           	           		<div id="category-title" class="nivo-html-caption">            	<strong>Category Pages</strong><br/>These pages display all the products in the category with a brief description and a link to a more detailed product page.  I also included a secondary navigation that allows the user to quickly switch between categories.</div>            	            	 <div id="product-title" class="nivo-html-caption">            	<strong>Product Pages</strong><br/>Each product has it's own page that displays information regarding cooking, weight, and description.</div>        	   